* '''Butler Jarvis:''' Good day, [sir/madam].<!--If pronoun is they/them he just says "Good day."-->
* '''Player:''' Hello. I'm helping Lord Hosidius find his missing son. I was wondering if you could help me.
* '''Butler Jarvis:''' I'm afraid I know not where Artur has gone. I do not speak to him much. He keeps himself to himself.
* '''Butler Jarvis:''' However, I've noticed him speaking to Olivia before. Maybe she can help.
* '''Player:''' Great, thanks.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Butler Jarvis again===
