* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Elena Hosidius===
* '''Player:''' Hello. I...
* '''Elena Hosidius:''' You're the one helping to find our son.
* '''Player:''' Yes I...
* '''Elena Hosidius:''' It's good that you're here to help. Artur is a good lad, but he does have a habit of biting off more than he can chew.
* '''Player:''' I was wondering if...
* '''Elena Hosidius:''' He's meant for greatness you know. He'll be a king one day.
* '''Player:''' Don't you mean...
