* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Chef Olivia===
* '''Player:''' Hello, I'm helping Lord Hosidius find his missing son. I was wondering if you had any idea where he might have gone?
* '''Chef Olivia:''' I'm sorry, but I don't know anything.
* '''Player:''' Are you sure?
* '''Chef Olivia:''' Well... I err...
* '''Player:''' Err?
* '''Chef Olivia:''' Oh this is awful. Please don't tell Lord Hosidius. He'll fire me if he finds out.
* '''Player:''' Calm down, you have nothing to fear from me. I just want to help find Artur. Do you know where he is?
* '''Chef Olivia:''' Artur and I, we're...
* '''Player:''' You're in love aren't you?
* '''Chef Olivia:''' Yes...
* '''Player:''' Well don't worry, your secret is safe with me.
* '''Chef Olivia:''' Thank you. Before he went missing, Artur told me he was going to find the original copy of the Royal Accord of Twill. That's where he will have gone.
* '''Chef Olivia:''' He's been spending a lot of time in the Arceuus Library recently, researching the Accord. He mentioned a librarian called Galana. Maybe she can help you.
* '''Player:''' Thank you.
* '''Chef Olivia:''' Please bring Artur back.
* {{tact|end}}

====Talking to Chef Olivia again====
* '''Chef Olivia:''' Please bring Artur back.
* '''Player:''' Where should I be looking again?
* '''Chef Olivia:''' He's been spending a lot of time in the Arceuus Library. He mentioned a librarian called Galana. Maybe she can help you.
* '''Player:''' Thank you.
* {{tact|end}}

==The Envoy to Varlamore==
===Talking to Galana===
* '''Galana:''' Do you need something?
* '''Player:''' I'm looking for information on the Royal Accord of Twill.
* '''Galana:''' The Royal Accord of Twill was signed by the heads of Kourend's five houses, known then as the Royal Lords. This was over a thousand years ago.
* '''Galana:''' The Accord declared that they would take over rulership of Great Kourend from the Council of Elders.
* '''Galana:''' For many years after the Accord was signed, the Royal Lords took it in turns to rule the kingdom. Each of them ruled for ten years in turn.
* '''Galana:''' Those practices have long since been abolished though and Kourend is now ruled by the Kourend Council. The original Accord has since been lost, but copies still exist in this library.
* '''Player:''' What if I wanted to find the original?
* '''Galana:''' Many have tried and failed. You would likely have no better luck. However, if it interests you, you might wish to read The Envoy to Varlamore, by Deryk Paulson.
* '''Galana:''' It details how the original Accord was lost.
* '''Player:''' Do you know where I can find the book?
* '''Galana:''' Try the [top/middle/bottom] floor, [north/south] [eastern/western] bay.
* '''Player:''' Thank you.
* {{tact|end}}

====Talking to Galana again====
* '''Player:''' Could you remind me where I can find that book on the Accord?
* '''Galana:''' Try the [top/middle/bottom] floor, [north/south] [eastern/western] bay.
