* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Elena Hosidius after Artur returns===
* '''Elena Hosidius:''' Thank you for finding our son. You've done this kingdom a great service.
* '''Player:''' It's no...
* '''Elena Hosidius:''' I do wonder if his father could have done more though. My brother would have had the entire army out searching.
* '''Player:''' Your brother...
* '''Elena Hosidius:''' My brother is Lord Shiro Shayzien. He commands the Shayzien Army. A luxury my husband doesn't have.
* '''Player:''' So you...
* '''Elena Hosidius:''' Maybe it doesn't always have to be that way. Things may well soon be different. Now be on your way, I have things to do.
* {{tact|end}}

